{
  "stem": "543.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Bell, and she said, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said maybe they, they do-- they did something, they put something in you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So Irving spoke to somebody from the-- from the Dutch government, and they wrote a letter back from Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, when you had-- when you had one injection, and you was bleeding, and it was all open and there was blisters, they couldn't work on you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to heal up first.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So between, it was maybe two, three-- two months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there were more people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes they, they try to-- you know--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of them died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know-- and, and, you know what also, not only that you didn't get enough-- all those things, you didn't get enough to eat either.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, we know that later in that time-- we knew that the-- that, that gas chambers were our showers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one time, the doctors were complaining to the-- to the-- to the block that the women were smelling.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And  he said, I want to have to give them a bath.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you imagine what a-- what a panic it was to give us a bath?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to go to a shower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We cry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not for sure they going to kill us, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Um.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every day, I was afraid to, to die.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it never let off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You always-- you don't go today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So many people died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I saw so many people dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were in Block 10, actually in prison.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not-- some people in the block who could walk out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But nobody's supposed to know what happened in Block 10.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, for hours, and hours, and hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
